            <div type="apparatus">
               <listApp>
                   <app><note>text based upon photographs</note></app>
                   <app loc="line 1"><note>Sofia 2018: [---]ωι[---]; the final vertical could either be iota or the first stroke of a nu; it is uncertain if any letters may have been lost beyond this.</note></app>
